Why do you want to look into it again?

52
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:17,320
Who was decided as the criminal?

53
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:19,560
What was the poison?
Was it thoroughly investigated?

54
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,160
Since the head chef

55
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,960
Dong Lingniang went missing,

56
