87
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,040
You're awake.

88
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,360
Stool.

89
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,720
Stool,

90
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,080
thank you for today.

91
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,320
If it weren't for you,

92
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,400
I would have lost my life.

93
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,400
It's alright.

94
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:21,120
You saved my life
outside the palace before.

95
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:22,640
Besides,

96
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,760
if you were to die,

97
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,360
who would cook for me?

98
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:32,440
Still saying such things
at a time like this.

99
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:38,960
What's wrong with you?

100
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:45,880
I...

101
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,400
I've managed to survive,

102
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,520
but I have offended Ms. Jia.

103
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:54,440
I'm afraid I can't go back anymore.

104
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,920
It's fine not to go back to that place.

105
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,240
You don't understand.

106
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,600
The Royal Kitchen is there.

107
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:09,280
It's my biggest dream in life.

108
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:13,440
Dream?

109
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,360
I love cooking.

110
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,760
I want to become the best chef
in the Royal Kitchen

111
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,720
and find
the supreme flavor in the world.

112
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:24,800
The supreme flavor in the world?

113
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,920
What is that?

114
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,440
My master told me

115
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:33,640
a chef's greatest aspiration was to find

116
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,640
the supreme flavor in the world.

117
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,880
But now I have nothing.

118
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:54,800
Perhaps you still have a chance
to return to the palace

119
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,400
to fulfill your dream.

120
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,920
Don't comfort me anymore.

121
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:03,160
I'm certain I can't go back.

122
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:06,800
You can choose to trust me once.

123
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:17,280
Well, what about your dream?

124
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,600
I...

